Ask HN: Create Videos from Your Screenshots
text:
Laurent here: I’m building a web app that helps you create beautiful videos from a screenshot or PDF.

Because I noticed the most engaging posts on social media often involve a video with smooth motion.

Would you use this for work or social media?

I’ve put together a landing page with sample videos generated by the tool, see https://screenrun.app/
